# Priya — Multilingual Voice Collections Agent
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# This is a no-code n8n build: secrets are stored as n8n Credentials,
# not environment variables. This file documents what you need.
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# Sarvam AI API key — get one at https://dashboard.sarvam.ai
# Used in TWO n8n Header Auth credentials:
#   1) Header "api-subscription-key: <key>"      -> STT + TTS nodes (2, 5, 7a)
#   2) Header "Authorization: Bearer <key>"      -> Chat Completions nodes (6, 8a)
SARVAM_API_KEY=

# Google Sheets (CRM stand-in) — authorized via n8n's built-in
# "Sign in with Google" OAuth on node 9. No key needed here.
# Sheet name: Sunrise_Collections_CRM - https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NhDuriRf7-jv3Ee5B0QHxacKATQ5PlheAR0gZ-n_x7Q/edit?usp=sharing


# Google Drive (telephony simulation) — customer audio clips are fetched
# via public "Anyone with the link" URLs. No key needed here.
# Hinglish - https://drive.google.com/file/d/10S3AEN0VcEdsYBIVf31aU2c7XOMz1GU2/view?usp=drive_link
# Tanglish - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EP45YrffY30CGh60WF1OcQS79Towpsgb/view?usp=sharing
